{"tid":518240,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[求大神]想搵返隻小學雞年代既PS2 GAME","createTime":"2018-01-03T06:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T18:02:39.000Z","uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9760a4e41bd2c18d47408a6501b55acae4a1b74","tid":518240,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:15:52.000Z","msg":"果陣仲係小學雞,去人地屋企玩PS2<br />\n果隻GAME係一入到去就渣住架車<br />\n然後個十字路口/D公路有勁多勁多車行緊<br />\n仲會有D好大型既車..泥頭車..木頭車等<br />\n你既目標係渣住架車飛出去,撞埋去引起連環交通意外....<br />\n愈多車炒愈高分...果陣玩好爽...但完全唔記得咩名<br />\n有冇大神玩過?? 而家PS4既年代仲有冇而隻GAME? PC呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981aea32c38cee3b2c14d9dea3e51d136fe24d74","tid":518240,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"我唔知佢有冇其他MODE,但我印象中係冇賽車既元素<br />\n得撞車鬥高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9100f2d1520b2c618c3c5c3c1c693f4e28aa35c5","tid":518240,"uid":15368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"981aea32c38cee3b2c14d9dea3e51d136fe24d74","tid":518240,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"我唔知佢有冇其他MODE,但我印象中係冇賽車既元素<br />\n得撞車鬥高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"屋企有碟 以前成日玩<br />\n今晚返屋企睇完話你知"},{"pid":"3a64e35edcdd48c992836c2681b3ad315b9ee1b7","tid":518240,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"我玩過PS2個隻又係咁上下<br />\n不過有賽車mode 撞爛人架車會有火加速 x1 x2 x3火咁 <br />\n<br />\n跟住就係你個個炒車mode咁 炒左車都可以碌多陣去hi側邊d車等佢炒 <br />\n<br />\n今晚返屋企俾名你睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5017da0ae706456fdbd00cbe58b949956a94b6","tid":518240,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"google同youtube同steam搵完<br />\n<br />\n隻GAME 叫burnout <br />\n<br />\n但有好多系列<br />\n<br />\n好似burnout 3: takedown (ps2) 先至有trailer trash mode (即係撞車鬥高分)<br />\n<br />\nSTEAM果隻burnout: paradise city 得賽車MODE??? 但我想玩trailer trash mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇大神玩緊,話我知有冇"},{"pid":"2d90c43bd6abe1033b405037100bd73f50a2d472","tid":518240,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"唔知"},{"pid":"6a8aeba81ad6b24aea28f9591d014a263d2e36e5","tid":518240,"uid":78222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>google同youtube同steam搵完<br />\n<br />\n隻GAME 叫burnout <br />\n<br />\n但有好多系列<br />\n<br />\n好似burnout 3: takedown (ps2) 先至有trailer trash mode (即係撞車鬥高分)<br />\n<br />\nSTEAM果隻burnout: paradise city 得賽車MODE??? 但我想玩trailer trash mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇大神玩緊,話我知有冇</blockquote><br />\nsteam個隻買左 好悶 對比ps2個隻超無癮 淨係賽車或者競時賽  有飄移拎分模式<br />\n雖然有電單車玩 但係得競時賽<br />\n車款黎講甚至係ps2版仲好玩<br />\n<br />\n個陣都試過用ps2模擬器玩返 但係玩玩下第一關就一定輕機無得繼續玩 好撚sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5196f2ddd63a63dd4ff1f8f982b6c2c02c408820","tid":518240,"uid":69873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"Burnt out 好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}